{
  "comment": "Per-device-type syslog catalog for Cisco IOS devices. Overlays the universal catalog (extends=true default): universal interface-up/interface-down/auth-* entries carry through; Cisco-format entries are added alongside. All entries use Class-1-only template vocabulary (no User/SourceIP/RuleName — deferred to follow-up epic). Message bodies match the %FACILITY-SEVERITY-MNEMONIC: form IOS emits verbatim so OpenNMS syslogd UEI matchers tuned for Cisco strings fire correctly.",
